Package: propor
Title: Data for Wurman-Style Maps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Liam Thomas", family = "Bolton", email = "liamthomasbolton@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: propor is an R package for creating data for Wurman-style maps, a form of cartogram in which polygons 
             (e.g. circles, hexagons, squares) arranged in a grid are proportionally resized according to a specified 
             variable and visualised along with the original polygons for reference.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:    
    sf,
    dplyr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
